{"tid":284804,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（老癈死全家）剛剛係林村比兩個老癈呃錢","createTime":"2017-06-15T08:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T13:48:25.000Z","uid":98821,"like":2,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"98c2240b0ceb57ed6835ed4aa70aaff31cf23a70","tid":284804,"uid":98821,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:50:09.000Z","msg":"是咁的，剛剛同個朋友去完林村<br />\n門口就有2個老癈塞左疊野比我個朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就係咁講叫我地跟佢過去<br />\n我都知係呃水架啦 不過見佢寫住$60一套咁就諗住算啦<br />\n之後最離譜既係寫完野之後 佢竟然叫我地掉上樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲係咁強調佢地呢棵係真既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後佢收錢 竟然要成3百幾蚊<br />\n話掛上去又要幾錢點點點 <br />\n同話佢塞過黎果疊野入面係唔只一套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好啦 到最後 雖然咁多位智商超過一千既巴打一定唔會好似我地咁蠢比人呃 但上黎都係想提醒一下大家唔送錢比老癈洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw我就唔怕得罪人既 老癈死全家 林村縱容老癈一樣死全村<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n冇錯係死全村呀"},{"pid":"64f72e80c7120624e5992df6b0dd55569b565366","tid":284804,"uid":48631,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:53:24.000Z","msg":"你係唔怕得罪人既就當場搞大件事佢啦,洗乜上黎鳩up呀"},{"pid":"91a20b3b4e3cd4837e2f4d9ea9fcef1fbbaa2d5e","tid":284804,"uid":98821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:05:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係唔怕得罪人既就當場搞大件事佢啦,洗乜上黎鳩up呀</blockquote><br />\n我果3舊水事小 我係要佢以後無錢賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b113625cc332d9192ea3da400298712c7b6cd2af","tid":284804,"uid":24034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:07:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你係唔怕得罪人既就當場搞大件事佢啦,洗乜上黎鳩up呀</blockquote><br />\n我果3舊水事小 我係要佢以後無錢賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9978543593258a9e4b83a3ad858d601ea22f21c3","tid":284804,"uid":96002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:09:57.000Z","msg":"日撚日都有你呢啲on9仔，好難冇錢賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4016bd221a3c93c28e1da693fe2a05c771167e5f","tid":284804,"uid":98821,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:10:34.000Z","msg":"邊個留負皮唔出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3d24a70956d503b00da2e39bd4b5ef6e44a555","tid":284804,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:10:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你係唔怕得罪人既就當場搞大件事佢啦,洗乜上黎鳩up呀</blockquote><br />\n我果3舊水事小 我係要佢以後無錢賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好得罪樓主呀,有仇必報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw,想問你用咩方法令佢以後冇錢賺?就係唔通係靠上黎連登開post唱衰佢咁陰毒🤔"},{"pid":"53dd6dfa5f9ed6b969adac2b89941f984270da23","tid":284804,"uid":56636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:11:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你係唔怕得罪人既就當場搞大件事佢啦,洗乜上黎鳩up呀</blockquote><br />\n我果3舊水事小 我係要佢以後無錢賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你當場數臭佢再上黎唱衰佢 連你嗰浸都賺唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df6de2968793a2809170a61dae8854fe48357b8","tid":284804,"uid":98821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:12:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日撚日都有你呢啲on9仔，好難冇錢賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多啲好似巴打咁醒既人 冇比錢人賺咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17901189c758