斤變兩都識報警唔俾錢喇</blockquote><br />\n都係果句 我報警拎返小小錢有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 靠你地把口 等多啲人睇到 聽到先有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以多謝你個留先"},{"pid":"fcbf8901233f622471cc684906ab3db6bde46e23","tid":284804,"uid":1581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:32:55.000Z","msg":"樓主起網上就串柒柒，現實就碌撚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33de28d9a66e6a9f0e5874d1ea172a740331a8cf","tid":284804,"uid":98821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:37:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主起網上就串柒柒，現實就碌撚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點碌撚發呀 絲打平時買野唔比錢咁威架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲未比人拉咩"},{"pid":"b2033266cf4af45bf0398d3dbb9b6a680152fd60","tid":284804,"uid":98821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:46:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主起網上就串柒柒，現實就碌撚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋 想再講多句 個個上網講野都比你話係現實碌撚 仲有咩意思 唔該你啦 人人係到講 你就跟住講 好得意咩 用下個腦批判下先再講啦 個個post一式一樣話人網上就點點點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79867dd6e208416ea3f887f8bb5ea48623eb4e84","tid":284804,"uid":1581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:47:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主起網上就串柒柒，現實就碌撚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋 想再講多句 個個上網講野都比你話係現實碌撚 仲有咩意思 唔該你啦 人人係到講 你就跟住講 好得意咩 用下個腦批判下先再講啦 個個post一式一樣話人網上就點點點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係網上兇狠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}